== 任務概要 ==

=== 發射準備 ===
[[File:Dawn_launch.jpg|left]][[卡纳维拉尔角空军基地17号航天发射复合体|17B號太空發射複合體]]由[[三角洲二號運載火箭|三角洲二號7925H]]發射昇空]]

黎明號在2007年9月27日於[[卡納維爾角空軍基地|卡納維爾角空軍基地]][[卡纳维拉尔角空军基地17号航天发射复合体|17B號太空發射複合體]]由[[三角洲二號運載火箭|三角洲二號7925H]]發射昇空<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/launchingrockets/status/2007/elvstatus-20070511.html|title=Expendable Launch Vehicle Status Report|date=2007-05-11|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2017-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623162426/https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/launchingrockets/status/2007/elvstatus-20070511.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。黎明號原先的發射時間為6月20日，但是因為許多因素干擾而延遲三個月之久。

探測器在2007年4月10日運抵位於[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[泰特斯维尔_(佛罗里达州)|泰特斯维尔]]的Astrotech公司，準備發射升空<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spaceflightnow.com/news/n0704/10dawnarrival/|title=Dawn arrives in Florida|author=NASA|publisher=Spaceflight Now|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2018-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031091149/https://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0704/10dawnarrival/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.space.gs/11-apr-2007-dawn.html|title=Dawn at Astrotech's Payload Processing Facility|publisher=Space and Astronautics News|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927205639/http://www.space.gs/11-apr-2007-dawn.html|archivedate=2007-09-27}}</ref>。黎明號原先的發射時間預計為6月20日，但是因為運輸問題延遲至6月30日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://space.newscientist.com/article/dn12215-launch-of-dawn-asteroid-mission-postponed-again.html|title=Launch of Dawn asteroid mission postponed again|publisher=NewScientistSpace|access-date=2012-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017180702/http://space.newscientist.com/article/dn12215-launch-of-dawn-asteroid-mission-postponed-again.html|archive-date=2007-10-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。因為用來吊起[[固體火箭助推器|固體火箭助推器]]的起重機發生故障，所以發射時間推延至7月7日。不過第二節火箭在6月15日已經成功安裝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.floridatoday.com/floridatoday/blogs/spaceteam/2007/06/pad-17a-to-be-fixed-mid-week.html|title=Pad 17 crane to be fixed mid-week|publisher=Florida Today|access-date=2012-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070917103023/http://www.floridatoday.com/floridatoday/blogs/spaceteam/2007/06/pad-17a-to-be-fixed-mid-week.html|archive-date=2007-09-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/launchingrockets/status/2007/elvstatus-20070618.html|title=Expendable Launch Vehicle Status Report|date=2007-06-18|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2017-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623162250/https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/launchingrockets/status/2007/elvstatus-20070618.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。發射時間後來為了避開[[鳳凰號|鳳凰號]]的預計發射窗口，而繼續推延。鳳凰號後來在8月4日成功發射升空。

=== 發射 ===

黎明號的發射時間重新設置在2007年9月26日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/dawn/news/HQ_07150_Dawn_postpone_Sep.html|title=NASA Mission to Asteroid Belt Rescheduled for September Launch|date=2007-07-07|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2017-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501120258/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/dawn/news/HQ_07150_Dawn_postpone_Sep.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/missions/highlights/schedule.html|title=Dawn Launch Date|work=NASA launch schedule|accessdate=2007-09-01|archive-date=2011-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110218005402/http://www.nasa.gov/missions/highlights/schedule.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然後因為天氣不佳，再度延後到隔天。9月27日發射窗口為07:20至07:49 EDT之間<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/launchingrockets/status/2007/elvstatus-20070907.html|title=Expendable Launch Vehicle Status Report|date=2007-09-07|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2017-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623162100/https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/launchingrockets/status/2007/elvstatus-20070907.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。黎明號最終於07:34 EDT由三角洲二號7925H順利發射升空<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ulalaunch.com/images/product_sheet/Delta_Product_Sheet_FINAL.pdf|title=ULA—One Team for Assured Access to Space|publisher=ulalaunch.com|accessdate=2008-03-04|format=PDF|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928093124/http://www.ulalaunch.com/images/product_sheet/Delta_Product_Sheet_FINAL.pdf|archivedate=2007-09-28|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/dawn/launch/index.html|title=NASA's Launch Coverage|date=2007-09-27|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2010-03-21|archive-date=2017-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624120420/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/dawn/launch/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/dawn/news/dawn-20070927.html|title=Dawn Spacecraft Successfully Launched|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2010-03-21|archive-date=2017-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515230530/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/dawn/news/dawn-20070927.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，速度為每秒11.46[[公里|公里]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www-ssc.igpp.ucla.edu/dawn/DawnJournal_24August08.html | title = Dear Dawnivores | date = 2008-08-24 | accessdate = 2010-03-21 | first = Marc D. | last = Rayman | archive-date = 2012-05-30 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20120530164742/www-ssc.igpp.ucla.edu/dawn/DawnJournal_24August08.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 巡航 ===

[[File:Mars_image_by_Dawn_probe.jpg|thumb]]]]

黎明號升空之後，[[離子推力器|離子推力器]]開始運作，於2007年12月17日開始進入巡航階段<ref>{{cite web | url = http://dawn.jpl.nasa.gov/mission/journal_12_17_07.asp | title = Dawn Journal: December 17, 2007 | last = Rayman | first = Marc D. | publisher = JPL | accessdate = 2010-03-21 | archive-date = 2009-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090712161248/http://dawn.jpl.nasa.gov/mission/journal_12_17_07.asp | dead-url = no }}</ref>。黎明號在2008年10月31日完成首次噴射，讓探測器前往[[火星|火星]]，目的是在2009年2月依賴火星的[[重力助推|重力助推]]前往小行星帶。

黎明號在2009年2月17日以549公里近距離通過火星附近，順利完成重力助推<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.planetary.org/blog/article/00001755/ | title = Dawn Journal: Aiming away from a bull's eye at Mars | accessdate = 2010-03-21 | first = Marc D. | last = Rayman | publisher = The Planetary Society | archive-date = 2011-07-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110716023248/http://www-ssc.igpp.ucla.edu/dawn/DawnJournal_24August08.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.space.com/missionlaunches/090218-dawn-asteroid-mars.html | title =Asteroid-Bound Probe Zooms Past Mars | publisher =Space.com | first =Tariq | last =Malik | date =2009-02-18 | accessdate =2010-03-21 | archive-date =2010-03-27 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20100327123433/http://www.space.com/missionlaunches/090218-dawn-asteroid-mars.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。探測器在同一天進入[[安全模式|安全模式]]，導致部份資料流失。黎明號在兩天之後解除安全模式，不過對於後續計劃沒有影響。這次事件的[[根本原因|根本原因]]為[[軟體|軟體]]程式錯誤所造成的<ref name=jplstatus>{{cite web
| url=http://dawn.jpl.nasa.gov/mission/status.asp
| date=2009-02-28
| accessdate=2009-08-04
| title=Dawn Receives Gravity Assist from Mars
| publisher=NASA/JPL
